H0.text: High winds are an event during a storm at sea that can add oxygen from the atmosphere to ocean water.

H1.text: Lightning is an event during a storm at sea that can add oxygen from the atmosphere to ocean water.

H3.text: Temperature change during a storm at sea can add oxygen from the atmosphere to ocean water.
